Items.Name: Doors
Items.Description: Mod adds everyone you see in the image above to the game. After downloading, you will be asked to open the mod using the Melon game. Usually the mod is automatically added to the game. If you do not see the Melon game in the list of programs, you need to use the guide button located in the upper right corner and follow the instructions that you will find in this page.
